Just to feel good just for a little while. When you 
feel so bad and so let down from everything, from

25:19.456 --> 25:31.432
everything around you, then that high for a little 
while has worked quite a bit. We had the opium

25:31.452 --> 25:33.575
problem. We found a civilian one night that had an 
estimated $3 million worth of opium. We weren't

25:40.143 --> 25:41.285
allowed to keep it. We wasn't allowed to follow it 
up. We thought it was fixing to be loaded on a

25:43.888 --> 25:47.573
civilian aircraft. We weren't allowed to follow 
it up for, I don't know why, but we wanted to find out

25:48.211 --> 25:54.037
where it was going. And then we took it back to 
headquarters and the Vietnamese QC, Quang Cong,

25:55.098 --> 26:00.524
took it away from us. And they allowed them to take 
it from us. They wouldn't have taken it from us if we

26:03.827 --> 26:09.173
hadn't have just given it to them. But we weren't 
going to. And it was almost fixing to cause a a war

26:14.097 --> 26:16.460
right there. Right. But we were ordered to give the 
opium to them. And I'm sure they either sold it or

26:22.847 --> 26:27.091
used it. You mentioned a while back about the 
Purple Heart. This guy got the Purple Heart one

26:31.916 --> 26:34.079
actually. He should have received medals for... 
