26:41.307 --> 26:42.568
Well, there was a high... There's

26:42.987 --> 27:00.136
a lot of guys that

26:42.987 --> 27:00.136
got medals for doing all kinds of stuff. I knew a guy 
that got the Medal of Honor. And he told me that he,

27:02.393 --> 27:04.115
you know. He said they needed a hero. So he got the 
Medal of Honor. So he didn't feel like he really

27:08.681 --> 27:11.184
didn't feel like he really. I feel like he probably 
did, but he doesn't feel like he deserves the Medal

27:11.304 --> 27:16.291
of Honor. Didn't know he was going to get it until he 
seen the states thought he's going to get

27:16.311 --> 27:20.296
reprimanded. He was in charge of the helicopter 
outfit. And they had a bunch of helicopters that

27:24.501 --> 27:27.985
made an attack in the DMZ. And when they did, Every 
helicopter he had got shot at, including his, and

27:30.659 --> 27:37.467
lost a lot of men. Do you remember his name? No, I 
