29:31.947 --> 29:32.548
received. Did you get a purple heart? No, I didn't. 
You didn't get wounded? That's too fast. I run

29:37.896 --> 29:40.259
backwards too fast. You asked me about fragging. 
Yeah, and you didn't know what I meant. I didn't

29:45.447 --> 29:53.779
until you explained to me what it was, but I didn't 
see that happen.

