I had a sergeant. We had to pull what they called a 
QRT, which was a quick reaction team. And what it

30:04.271 --> 30:07.475
was, if we came under attack, we were the first ones 
out. And we had a sergeant that wouldn't lead us.

30:12.820 --> 30:14.742
The reason he wouldn't was because he was afraid 
to. Probably I would have, I hate to say this now,

30:15.683 --> 30:23.732
but a few years ago it wouldn't bother me, but I 
would have probably shot that sergeant. if I'd

30:24.404 --> 30:26.888
ever got the chance. But like I said, my hole 
